#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ksnakeduel; is a simple snake duel game. You can play against the computer "
"or a friend. The aim of the game is to live longer than your opponent. To do "
"that, avoid running into a wall, your own tail and that of your opponent."
msgstr ""
"&ksnakeduel; je preprosta igra kačjih dvobojev. Igrate lahko proti "
"računalniku ali prijatelju. Cilj igre je živeti dlje od nasprotnika. Če "
"želite to narediti, se izogibajte trčenju v steno, v svoj rep in "
"nasprotnikov rep."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ksnakeduel; is a simple Snake-like game. The aim is to survive as long as "
"possible and eat as many fruits as you can."
msgstr ""
"&ksnakeduel; je preprosta igra, podobna kači. Cilj je preživeti čim dlje in "
"pojesti čim več sadja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can switch between these games using the game type selector in the "
"configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Med tema igrama lahko preklapljate z izbirnikom vrste igre v "
"konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playing &ksnakeduel;"
msgstr "Igranje &ksnakeduel;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:105 index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rules"
msgstr "Pravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once a round is started, the players do not stop moving forward (unless the "
"game is paused). All you have to do is avoid crashing by changing your "
"players direction. Additionally you can try to hinder your opponent. For "
"this it is possible to increase the velocity by pressing your accelerator "
"key."
msgstr ""
"Ko se krog začne, se igralci ne nehajo premikati naprej (razen če je igra "
"začasno ustavljena). Vse kar morate storiti je, da se izognete zrušitvi "
"tako, da spremenite smer igralcev. Poleg tega lahko poskušate ovirati "
"nasprotnika. Za to je možno povečati hitrost s pritiskom na tipko za "
"pospeševanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A round starts when all human players press a direction key. The initial "
"moving direction is then in this direction."
msgstr ""
"Runda se začne, ko vsi človeški igralci pritisnejo smerno tipko. Začetna "
"smer gibanja je potem v tej smeri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to interrupt playing, select the <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item. Additionally the game is paused when the game loses "
"the keyboard focus, &eg; when switching to an other window."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prekiniti igranje, izberite <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo "
"action=\"simul\"><keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem> Zaustavi</guimenuitem></menuchoice> element menija. "
"Poleg tega se igra začasno ustavi, ko igra izgubi fokus tipkovnice, &eg;. ko "
"preklopite na drugo okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126 index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To continue the game, select again this menu item or hit the keyboard "
"shortcut. The game will also continue if you press one of the direction "
"keys. But be careful, your player switches to this direction immediately."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nadaljevati z igro, znova izberite ta element menija ali "
"pritisnite bližnjico na tipkovnici. Igra se bo nadaljevala tudi, če "
"pritisnete eno od smernih tipk. Vendar bodite previdni, vaš igralec takoj "
"preklopi v to smer."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A game consists of several rounds, and ends if a player has at least nine "
"points, and additionally two more points than the opponent. The current "
"score is always displayed in the status bar."
msgstr ""
"Igra je sestavljena iz več rund in se konča, če ima igralec najmanj devet "
"točk in dodatno dve točki več od nasprotnika. Trenutni rezultat je vedno "
"prikazan v vrstici stanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138 index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the difficulty level of the game using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Difficulty</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> submenu or the drop-down box on the status bar. The difficulty "
"influences the speed of the game and the computer player."
msgstr ""
"Težavnostno stopnjo igre lahko spremenite v podmeniju "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Težavnost</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> ali v spustnem polju v vrstici stanja. Težavnost "
"vpliva na hitrost igre in računalniškega igralca."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Computer Player"
msgstr "Računalniški predvajalnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can play against a computer. The difficulty level of the game influences "
"the intelligence of the computer player."
msgstr ""
"Igrate lahko proti računalniku. Težavnostna stopnja igre vpliva na "
"inteligenco računalniškega igralca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At low levels the computer doesn't care about the opponent and just moves "
"around. At higher skill levels the computer tries to hinder the opponent "
"when he comes near."
msgstr ""
"Na nizkih ravneh se računalnik ne ozira na nasprotnika in se samo premika. "
"Na višjih ravneh znanja poskuša računalnik ovirati nasprotnika, ko se "
"približa."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Keyboard"
msgstr "Uporaba tipkovnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each player has five keys. Four keys for changing the direction and one to "
"accelerate."
msgstr ""
"Vsak igralec ima pet tipk. Štiri tipke za spreminjanje smeri in ena za "
"pospeševanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The direction keys do not have to be held down. Simply press them once to "
"change the direction of your player."
msgstr ""
"Smernih tipk ni treba držati pritisnjenih. Preprosto jih enkrat pritisnite, "
"da spremenite smer predvajalnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Acceleration only occurs while the acceleration key remains depressed. When "
"you release the acceleration key, velocity returns to normal."
msgstr ""
"Pospeševanje se pojavi le, ko je tipka za pospeševanje pritisnjena. Ko "
"spustite tipko za pospeševanje, se hitrost vrne v normalno stanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179 index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/shortcuts.html\">alter the keys</"
"ulink> using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/shortcuts.html\">Tipke lahko spremenite</"
"ulink> z uporabo <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> v elementu menija "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj bližnjice...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playing KSnake mode"
msgstr "Igranje v načinu KSnake"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the game is started, the player does not stop moving forward (unless "
"the game is paused). All you have to do is avoid crashing by changing your "
"direction. A game starts when you press a direction key. The initial moving "
"direction is then in this direction."
msgstr ""
"Ko se igra začne, igralec ne ustavi premikanja naprej (razen če je igra "
"začasno ustavljena). Vse kar morate storiti je, da se izognete trčenju tako, "
"da spreminjate svojo smer. Igra se začne, ko pritisnete smerno tipko. "
"Začetna smer gibanja je potem v tej smeri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to pause playing, select the <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo "
"action=\"simul\"><keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or hit the "
"keyboard shortcut. Additionally the game is paused when the game loses the "
"keyboard focus, &eg; when switching to an other window."
msgstr ""
"Če želite začasno ustaviti predvajanje, izberite <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Premor</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> element menija ali pritisnite bližnjico na tipkovnici. Poleg "
"tega se igra začasno ustavi, ko igra izgubi fokus tipkovnice, &eg; ko "
"preklopite na drugo okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the game there will always be a piece of fruit on the map. If you collect "
"it your score will increase with 5 points. The current score is always "
"displayed in the status bar."
msgstr ""
"V igri bo na zemljevidu vedno kos sadja. Če ga poberete, se bo vaš rezultat "
"povečal za 5 točk. Trenutni rezultat je vedno prikazan v vrstici stanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are moving through the map there will also appear obstacles. "
"Hitting them will also result in a crash. However, every time an obstacle "
"appears and you survive you'll be rewarded 2 points"
msgstr ""
"Ko se premikate po zemljevidu, se bodo pojavile tudi ovire. Če udarite "
"vanje, bo prišlo tudi do nesreče. Vendar vsakič, ko se pojavi ovira in "
"preživite, boste nagrajeni z 2 točkama"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the keyboard"
msgstr "Uporaba tipkovnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each player has four keys. These are used for changing the direction. The "
"direction keys do not have to be held down. Simply press them once to change "
"the direction of your player."
msgstr ""
"Vsak igralec ima štiri tipke. Uporabljajo se za spreminjanje smeri. Smernih "
"tipk ni treba držati pritisnjenih. Preprosto jih enkrat pritisnite, da "
"spremenite smer igralca."

