#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These shortcuts <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/shortcuts.html\">can be "
"changed</ulink> by selecting the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Te bližnjice <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/shortcuts.html\">lahko "
"spremenite</ulink> z izbiro elementa menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj bližnjice...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Configuration Dialog"
msgstr "Konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"&ksnakeduel;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item will open a further "
"dialog which lets you tweak &ksnakeduel;'s behavior."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &ksnakeduel;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, se "
"odpre nadaljnje pogovorno okno, ki vam omogoča prilagajanje vedenja "
"&ksnakeduel;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid "This dialog is divided into two pages."
msgstr "To pogovorno okno je razdeljeno na dve strani."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>General Configuration</title>"
msgstr "<title>Splošna konfiguracija</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure &ksnakeduel; - General"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte &ksnakeduel; - Splošno"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>General Configuration</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Splošna konfiguracija</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game type"
msgstr "Vrsta igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will let you change the game type. There are three options:"
msgstr "Tako boste lahko spremenili vrsto igre. Obstajajo tri možnosti:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:487
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ksnakeduel;: Player vs Player"
msgstr "&ksnakeduel;: Igralec proti igralcu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid "A &ksnakeduel; game between two human players."
msgstr "&ksnakeduel; igra med dvema človeškima igralcema."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ksnakeduel;: Player vs Computer"
msgstr "&ksnakeduel;: Igralec proti računalniku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "A &ksnakeduel; game between a human player and the computer."
msgstr "&ksnakeduel; igra med človeškim igralcem in računalnikom."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "KSnake mode: Single player"
msgstr "Način KSnake: en igralec"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid "A single player &ksnakeduel; game."
msgstr "En igralec igra &ksnakeduel;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disable acceleration"
msgstr "Onemogoči pospešek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking this box will disable the acceleration feature - pressing the "
"acceleration key will have no effect, both vehicles will always travel with "
"constant velocity."
msgstr ""
"Če potrdite to polje, boste onemogočili funkcijo pospeševanja – pritisk na "
"tipko za pospeševanje ne bo imel učinka, obe vozili bosta vedno vozili s "
"konstantno hitrostjo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:513
#, no-c-format
msgid "Player Names"
msgstr "Imena igralcev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify custom names to use for the players to override the use of default "
"ones."
msgstr ""
"Določite imena po meri, ki jih bodo uporabljali igralci, da preglasijo "
"uporabo privzetih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default name for player one is the name of the current logged in user."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto ime za prvega igralca je ime trenutno prijavljenega uporabnika."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Options"
msgstr "Možnosti igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify the <guilabel>Rounds to win:</guilabel> to define how many rounds "
"are required before a winner is declared."
msgstr ""
"Določite <guilabel>Runde za zmago:</guilabel>, da določite, koliko rund je "
"potrebnih, preden se razglasi zmagovalec."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Theme Configuration</title>"
msgstr "<title>Konfiguracija teme</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure &ksnakeduel; - Theme"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte &ksnakeduel; - Tema"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Theme Configuration</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracija teme</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid "This page will allow you to change the theme &ksnakeduel; uses."
msgstr ""
"Na tej strani boste lahko spremenili temo, ki jo &ksnakeduel; uporablja."

